                "invention-title": [
                    "Flue gas waste heat comprehensive utilization system under variable load of boiler",
                    "一种锅炉变负荷下烟气余热综合利用系统"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a flue gas waste heat comprehensive utilization system under variable load of a boiler. The flue gas waste heat comprehensive utilization system comprises a wind power generation device, a solar power generation device, a power station boiler, water electrolysis hydrogen production equipment, a control center and the like. After hydrogen is prepared by the water electrolysis hydrogen production equipment, the hydrogen is fed into a boiler burner for auxiliary combustion; the temperature measuring device and the flame intensity detecting device diagnose the flame combustion state, and obtained data are transmitted to the control center so as to adjust the fuel supply conditions of the water electrolysis hydrogen production equipment and the coal feeder. When the wind power generation device, the solar power generation device and the power station boiler are fully operated in a fire coal load mode, the water electrolysis hydrogen production device is driven to generate a large amount of hydrogen, the hydrogen reacts with nitrogen to produce ammonia after passing through the drying device and the deoxidizing device, and the ammonia is stored in the liquid ammonia storage tank after being pressurized and liquefied; and the ammonia gas is output outwards through the vaporizer when needing to be used. The problems of high carbon emission, poor low-load combustion stability and insufficient flue gas waste heat utilization in variable-load operation of an existing boiler are solved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种锅炉变负荷下烟气余热综合利用系统，包括风力发电装置、太阳能发电装置、电站锅炉、电解水制氢设备、控制中心等设备；电解水制氢设备制取氢气后，送入锅炉燃烧器进行辅助燃烧；测温装置和火焰强度检测装置对火焰燃烧状态进行诊断，得到的数据传输给控制中心以调节电解水制氢设备和给煤机的燃料供应情况；风力发电装置和太阳能发电装置和电站锅炉燃煤负荷充分运行时，驱动电解水制氢设备产生大量氢气，通过干燥设备和脱氧设备后，与氮气反应制取氨气，通过加压液化后贮存于液氨储罐内；需要使用氨气时通过汽化器向外输出。本发明解决了现有锅炉变负荷运行存在的碳排放高、低负荷燃烧稳定性差和烟气余热利用不充分的问题。"
                }
